metadata.name: Pepe Tuum Mobile
metadata.description:
Mechadelics #1

This famous Pepe mechanism produces an unlimited green diamond energy that people enjoy very much. It energizes everyone and its source is little known.  Physicists  still work on it...
Pepe works day and night to produce and radiate this magical energy and never gets tired.
It is rumored that Pepe tuum  will win the next Nobel Prize...

10 sec, 2000x2000, mp4
